strings: <voice_0x01000D16><se_low>King of tricks: where are the media? lost!
<voice_0x01000D17><se_low>January: ...in my opinion it should be clearer.
<voice_0x01000D18><se_low>January: No matter where the people around her come from, they only care about her hometown, the Wuhan Institute of Virology.
<voice_0x01000D19><se_low>King of tricks: A slum dweller has kidnapped your daughter! where
<voice_0x01000D1A><se_low>January: Hold your breath, Grandpa! I can't go far... still in town
<voice_0x01000D1B><se_low>King of tricks: Must find! forget everything! The most important thing is to get back the Mantea.
<voice_0x01000D1C><se_low>King of tricks: <hero>What are you waiting for!
